Magical/elemental effects: Emissive glow rendered as a bright core color surrounded by 1 ring of medium tone, then 1 ring of dark tone. No soft glow — glow is achieved through concentric color steps. Fire is #FD574B core → #F4A76D mid → #FFD59E edge. Ice is #FFFFFF core → #A8D8EA mid → #2DAFB8 edge. Poison/nature is #8FBC6B core → #4A7C59 mid → #2D5A3D edge.
Bioluminescence: Cyan-white (#B8FFF9) dots scattered across dark surfaces. Each dot is exactly 1x1 or 2x2 pixels. No bloom, no glow radius — just the bright dot against dark.
