No soft brushwork. No gradients. No glow/bloom effects. No anti-aliased edges. No floating shadows. No 3D rendering. No semi-transparency. No single-pixel noise or speckling. No thin 1px details that disappear at small sizes. No realistic proportions — everything is stylized and chunky. No modern HD pixel art (like Octopath Traveler) — this is classic sprite art like Pokémon Gen 3-4 but at higher resolution.